                An actual spork-turned-craft-project, Forky is pretty sure that he doesn’t belong in Bonnie's room.
                Unfortunately, every time he tries to get away, 
                Woody yanks him back into an adventure he’d rather skip.
                Forky is a toy that Bonnie made out of a disposable spork,
                so he’s facing a crisis. He wants to fulfill his purpose as a spork,
                but now has a new toy purpose thrust upon him.” 
            </p>
