                <div id="bop"> <h3>Bo Peep</h3><br/>
                  <img src="images/character_bopeep.jpg" align="left" width="160px">

           <p>
                Played by <a href="https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001633/"> Potts </a><br/>
                Bo is the romantic interest (later girlfriend) of Woody, 
                providing a calm and loving comfort whenever he is overwhelmed.
                She is noted for using her shepherdess crook to hook her cowboy 
                and bring him closer in a romantic way. In private, she is a great
                deal more daring with her words and actions, which Woody seems to be
                quite fond of. She and her sheep were bought along with the lamp not 
                too long after Molly was born, due to the baby being scared of the dark,
                which "broke every toy's heart", according to Woody. The lamp comforted 
                Molly and she would often have her hand lay on Bo's feet.
            </p>   
